    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248150/extras/41328828e1b843375b50bb0776e40865.poster.avif?t=1747764919\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248150/extras/41328828e1b843375b50bb0776e40865.webm?t=1747764919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248150/extras/41328828e1b843375b50bb0776e40865.mp4?t=1747764919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an Anchorite, the last line of defense for the survivors of Vestige, a city overrun by invaders from another dimension.  Take the fight to these vile mechanical creatures alone or with friends as you explore a dark stylized world and shoot, cast, and maneuver your way to victory!  Customize your character with a variety of guns, spells, and gear, and upgrade them to take on even greater challenges! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248150/extras/5c3af9de726cc5b086942e9cd3aba7af.poster.avif?t=1747764919\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248150/extras/5c3af9de726cc5b086942e9cd3aba7af.webm?t=1747764919\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248150/extras/5c3af9de726cc5b086942e9cd3aba7af.mp4?t=1747764919\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate and battle through the city of Vestige, solo or in a group of up to four players. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose your loadout with a point-buy system for diverse builds with meaningful trade-offs. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new equipment as you progress, and upgrade it with materials found in the world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achieve a high score by defeating enemies, finding loot, and finishing stages quickly. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get nostalgic with a retro-3D aesthetic reminiscent of the consoles of the late 90s. </p></li></ul>",
